QOwnNotes (notepad with markdown support and ownCloud integration)

QOwnNotes is the open source (GPL) plain-text file notepad with markdown
support and todo list manager for GNU/Linux, Mac OS X and Windows,
that (optionally) works together with the notes application of ownCloud.

- You own your own notes! All notes are stored as plain-text files
  on your desktop computer.

- Sync them over devices (desktop & mobile) with your ownCloud
  sync client.

- Use ownCloud Notes to edit your notes in the web.

Homepage: http://www.qownnotes.org/
Author:   Patrizio Bekerle <patrizio@bekerle.com>

